# ==============================================================================
# Asella Organic — Frontend Environment Variables
# ==============================================================================
# In development (npm run dev), you usually don't need this because Vite proxies
# all API calls to http://localhost:3001 automatically.
#
# In production, if your React app and Node API are hosted on the SAME domain
# (e.g. both on asellaorganic.com), you don't need this either. The browser
# will automatically route relative paths correctly.
#
# HOWEVER, if your Node API is on a DIFFERENT subdomain (e.g., api.asellaorganic.com)
# while your React app is on your main domain, you MUST define this variable so 
# Axios knows where to send requests.
# ==============================================================================

# VITE_API_URL=https://api.asellaorganic.com
